('Arithmetic Fundamentals', 'Decimals', 'Rounding decimals', 'Round the decimal to the nearest whole number.', 'Round 12.49 to the nearest whole number.', '12', '13', '12.4', '12.5', 'Look at the tenths place (4). Since it is <5, keep the ones place the same: 12.'),
('Arithmetic Fundamentals', 'Decimals', 'Rounding decimals', 'Round the decimal to the nearest tenth.', 'Round 8.25 to the nearest tenth.', '8.3', '8.2', '8.0', '8.5', 'Look at the hundredths place (5). Since it is ≥5, round the tenths place up: 8.2 → 8.3.'),
